snippet.title: Exploding Kittens - The Game | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Exploding Kittens is a multiplayer card game for people who are into kittens and explosions and laser beams and sometimes goats.

Play Exploding Kittens - The Game, on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81518722
